{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-7","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao sam zvuk i vežbovao sam izgovor početnih glasova i slogova.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-initials","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">m</span> je nosni zvuk. Da biste ga proizveli, nežno zatvorite usne kao da želite da kažete <span class=\"highlighted-text\">b</span>, ali umesto otvaranja usta, zatvorite ih i pustite da zvuk izađe kroz vaš nos dok blago pjevate grlom.</p>\n<p>Trebalo bi da se osećaš kao kada pevaš pesmu sa zatvorenim usnama, ispuštajući blag, kontinuiran nosni ton bez vazduha koji izlazi kroz tvoje usne.</p>\n<p>Ponekad možete čuti <span class=\"highlighted-text\">m</span> izgovoreno kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">mo</span>. To je zato što dodavanje <span class=\"highlighted-text\">o</span> na kraju čini ovaj početak zvučnijim/lakšim za slušanje.</p>\n<p>Kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">m</span> prati kraj <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">o</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span>, na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span>, dobija slogove: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ma</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">mo</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">mi</span>, na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">mu</span>.</p>\n<p>Kao što je sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">b</span>, kada izgovarate ove slogove, lako povezujete zvuk <span class=\"highlighted-text\">m</span> direktno do kraja bez pauza između njih. Jedina razlika će biti oblik usta koje napravite za svaki specifičan završetak.</p>\n<p>Pokušajte da izgovorite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">m</span> po ovim slogovima, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">mi</span> u različitim tonovima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Herufi</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">mī</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">眯</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">mí</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">迷</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">mǐ</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">米</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">mì</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">蜜</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-7"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company3-reception.png","characters":[{"character":"Wang Hua","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_pinyin_initials.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":126.66,"finishTimestamp":142.39},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.87,"dialogue":{"text":"m","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":3.05,"finishTime":3.89,"dialogue":{"text":"ma","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":4.87,"finishTime":5.81,"dialogue":{"text":"mo","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":6.58,"finishTime":7.54,"dialogue":{"text":"mi","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":8.45,"finishTime":9.4,"dialogue":{"text":"mu","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"star